  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of AMG 714 in Adult Patients With Type II Refractory Celiac Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of AMG 714 in Adult Patients With Type II Refractory Celiac Disease, an In Situ Small Bowel T Cell Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
